    "description": "One night, all GEOF members were called upon an urgent mission, an urban gang has grown strong in these past weeks and had managed to avoid the spotlight until recently.<br>Gather your squad, customize its equipment, choose your resources, dive into Mafia-controlled buildings, and fight through hordes of enemies to protect your city!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385660/extras/022faf7245de304a3c918eb785d391e0.poster.avif?t=1709183291\" width=624 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385660/extras/022faf7245de304a3c918eb785d391e0.webm?t=1709183291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385660/extras/022faf7245de304a3c918eb785d391e0.mp4?t=1709183291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FEATURES:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Customize your 5 squad member’s equipment to suit your strategy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385660/extras/248bba002aec6f81f4a0464cf36ea460.poster.avif?t=1709183291\" width=624 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385660/extras/248bba002aec6f81f4a0464cf36ea460.webm?t=1709183291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385660/extras/248bba002aec6f81f4a0464cf36ea460.mp4?t=1709183291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Fight through several rooms using covers to position yourself with advantage and flank the enemy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite